OL,3,CSouth West Water ordered to return
OL,4,Cmillions of pounds to customers
OL,6,FITV News' Marina Jenkins sent this
OL,7,Freport from Brixham
OL,9,FPeople in Brixham say they still don't
OL,10,Ftrust the quality of their water after
OL,11,FSouth West Water was ordered to return
OL,12,Fmore than #17million to customers for
OL,13,Ffailing to meet pollution targets.
OL,15,FRegulator Ofwat made the announcement
OL,16,Ffollowing its annual review of water
OL,17,Fcompany performances, with South West
OL,18,FWater (SWW) to return the money via
OL,19,Flower bills next year.
