OL,3,CSouth West Water ordered to return
OL,4,Cmillions of pounds to customers
OL,6,FIt comes just months after customers
OL,7,Fin Brixham were forced to boil their
OL,8,Fwater for weeks after an outbreak of
OL,9,Fcryptosporidiosis.
OL,11,FOfwat has recategorised SWW from
OL,12,F"lagging behind" to "average", but
OL,13,Fstill underperforming in some areas
OL,14,Flike pollution incidents and drinking
OL,15,Fwater quality.
OL,17,FToday's report highlighted that the
OL,18,Fperiod between 2022-2023 saw an 80%
OL,19,Fincrease in incidents - making SWW the
OL,20,Fworst-performing provider.
