OL,3,CSouth West Water ordered to return
OL,4,Cmillions of pounds to customers
OL,6,FGiles Bristow, CEO of campaign group
OL,7,FSurfers Against Sewage, said: "When
OL,8,Fare they going to learn and put the
OL,9,Fmoney to work that they're being given
OL,10,Fin customer bills and actually improve
OL,11,Fthe environment"?
OL,13,F"Last year across the country 2,000
OL,14,Fpeople let us know they got sick from
OL,15,Fgoing in the water. Many of those were
OL,16,Fin apparently excellent bathing waters
OL,17,Fand lots of those were in the South
OL,18,FWest."
