OL,3,CSouth West Water ordered to return
OL,4,Cmillions of pounds to customers
OL,6,FIn total, Ofwat has ordered water
OL,7,Fcompanies across England and Wales to
OL,8,Fpay back nearly #160m because of poor
OL,9,Fperformance, and also highlighted
OL,10,Fproblems in culture and leadership
OL,11,Fwith need for investment.
OL,13,FPennon Group, which owns SWW, said:
OL,14,F"Today, Ofwat confirmed that our
OL,15,FGroup's position is improving across
OL,16,Fall our businesses. But we know there
OL,17,Fis more work to be done.
